	<h2>QR Code in China</h2>
	<h4>QR Code now is been used so widely in China. Mainly 3 Ways to use it.</h4>
	<h3>Use QR Code to Pay</h3>
	<p>I belive that most of you heard about Alibaba or Tencent. This two Company is the first two company to lead this trend.</p>
	<img src="asset/qrcode_pay.jpg" alt= "QR Code Pay for a Coffee">
	<h5>Here is some data about it.</h5>
		<ol>
			<li>China Official Daily: More than 90% payment in China is completed via QR Code.</li>
			<li>Consulting Asso.:QR Code Payment in 2020Q4 is over RMB 1000 Billion</li>
			<li>China Gov.: 10 Billion QR Code is used in China <strong>Every Single Day</strong></li>
		</ol>
	<h3>Use QR Code as e-Ticket</h3>
	<img src="asset/qrcode_eticket.jpg" alt= "QR Code as Bording Pass">
	<h5>Here is some Comments.</h5>
		<ol>
			<li>Flight Passengers: "It is easier to carry and manage e-Ticket by QR Code".</li>
			<li>Football match Audience: "Fast and safe".</li>
		</ol>	
	<h3>Use QR Code against Covid-19</h3>
	<img src="asset/qrcode_health.jpeg" alt= "Use QR Code to record attendence">
	<h5>How China does.</h5>
		<ol>	
			<li>People are asked to show QR Code to record their journey when in Pubilc.</li>
			<li>Close with the Postive will get a Red QR Code.</li>
			<li>Red QR code are suggested to stay at home.</li>			
		</ol>
	<h2>Some different opinion</h2>
		<h3>Some holds an opinion that QR Code is not that safe.</h3>
		<ol>	
			<li>When QR Code is all used, what can we use?</li>
			<li>If QR code in Payment is guessed out, who can protect our money?</li>	
		</ol>
	<h3>Though there is a lot of concern about QR code, i still believe that QR Code Benefits People a lot.</h3>	
